> <OLD>
>
> There was a heavy SIGH of relief over from WHEELIE as air went out through
> the exhaust vents over around his cranial plating, a cool air rush blasting
> through his systems as he relaxed.  "Things here are not as they be, and
> that makes me quite uneasy.  I do not like where we do not is going on,
> someone is playing things to another throng.  Something on this planet is
> amiss, and we'll have to find it out or end up smashed like a hiss."
>
> WHEELIE glanced over at the other DINOBOTS then, hoping that they were all
> powering down their weapons and they could figure out what had happened.

<NEW>

The DINOBOTS were not powering down thier weapons, but then again as
they were in beastmode, their weapons were their teeth and claws.
However after a moment they did resume robot mode, and in this mode
their weapons were not in evidence.

"Me Grimlock say somehting is wrong. Me Grimlock want to smash little
Decepticon that did this to us!" GRIMLOCK smashed his fist into his
hand making a loud crunching sound.

The other DINOBOTS nodded as well, all looking to vent their anger on
something, anything.

"Grimlock!" BACKSTOP said as he approached. "You have reverted back to
normal?" He looked both surprised and relieved as he came up. He had
been flying in robot mode using somehting like a jet back and now he
was landing nearby.

GRIMLOCK nodded as he looked at BACKSTOP, "You did this?"

BACKSTOP nodded, "Yes, but it shouldn't have happened yet." He looked
thoroughly confused.

(TAG)

- Preston
